<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	</head>
	<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#0a0a0a;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,sans-serif;">

		<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#0a0a0a;padding:40px 20px;">
			<tr>
				<td align="center">
					<table
						width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#151515;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #2a2a2a;">

						{# Header #}
						<tr>
							<td style="padding:40px 40px 20px;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid #2a2a2a;">
								<h1 style="color:#6366F9;font-size:24px;margin:0;">Carte Blanche</h1>
							</td>
						</tr>

						{# Confirmation #}
						<tr>
							<td style="padding:40px;">

								<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
									<tr>
										<td align="center" style="padding-bottom:20px;">
											<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
												<tr>
													<td style="width:60px;height:60px;border-radius:30px;background-color:#14532d;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:28px;color:#22c55e;">
														&#10003;
													</td>
												</tr>
											</table>
										</td>
									</tr>
								</table>

								<h2 style="color:#ffffff;font-size:22px;text-align:center;margin:0 0 10px;">Paiement confirmé !</h2>
								<p style="color:#a1a1a1;text-align:center;margin:0 0 30px;font-size:15px;">
									Bonjour
									{{ user.firstName }}, votre commande a été validée.
								</p>
								<p style="color:#888;text-align:center;margin:-18px 0 28px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.45;">
									Vous trouverez en pièce jointe un PDF avec vos places et les QR codes (aucun lien vers le site n’est nécessaire pour les afficher).
								</p>

								{# Récapitulatif #}
								<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#1a1a1a;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #2a2a2a;margin-bottom:30px;">
									<tr>
										<td style="padding:20px;">
											<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
												<tr>
													<td style="color:#a1a1a1;font-size:13px;padding-bottom:10px;">Référence</td>
													<td style="color:#6366F9;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;text-align:right;padding-bottom:10px;">{{ order.reference }}</td>
												</tr>
												<tr>
													<td style="color:#a1a1a1;font-size:13px;padding-bottom:10px;">Date</td>
													<td style="color:#ffffff;font-size:13px;text-align:right;padding-bottom:10px;">{{ order.createdAt|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</td>
												</tr>
												<tr>
													<td style="color:#a1a1a1;font-size:13px;padding-bottom:10px;">Tickets</td>
													<td style="color:#ffffff;font-size:13px;text-align:right;padding-bottom:10px;">{{ order.tickets|length }}
														place(s)</td>
												</tr>
												<tr>
													<td colspan="2" style="border-top:1px solid #2a2a2a;padding-top:14px;">
														<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
															<tr>
																<td style="color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;">Total</td>
																<td style="color:#6366F9;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;text-align:right;">{{ order.totalAmount|number_format(0, ',', ' ') }}
																	€</td>
															</tr>
														</table>
													</td>
												</tr>
											</table>
										</td>
									</tr>
								</table>

								{# Tickets #}
								<h3 style="color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;margin:0 0 15px;">Vos tickets</h3>

								{% for ticket in order.tickets %}
									<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#1a1a1a;border-radius:8px;border:1px solid #2a2a2a;margin-bottom:12px;">
										<tr>
											<td style="padding:16px;">
												<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
													<tr>
														<td style="vertical-align:top;width:100%;">
															<p style="color:#6366F9;font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;margin:0 0 4px;font-weight:600;">
																{% if ticket.restaurant.categories is not empty %}
																	{{ ticket.restaurant.categories|first.name }}
																{% else %}
																	Restaurant
																{% endif %}
															</p>
															<p style="color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;margin:0 0 4px;">{{ ticket.restaurant.name }}</p>
															<p style="color:#a1a1a1;font-size:12px;margin:0 0 4px;">{{ ticket.restaurant.address }}</p>
															{% if ticket.restaurant.auctionDate %}
																<p style="color:#a1a1a1;font-size:12px;margin:0;">
																	{{ ticket.restaurant.auctionDate|date('d/m/Y') }}
																	{% if ticket.restaurant.auctionTime %}
																		à
																		{{ ticket.restaurant.auctionTime|date('H:i') }}
																	{% endif %}
																</p>
															{% endif %}
														</td>
														<td style="width:100px;text-align:center;vertical-align:top;padding-left:12px;">
															<p style="color:#6366F9;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;margin:0;">QR Code disponible dans<br>Mes réservations</p>
														</td>
													</tr>
												</table>
											</td>
										</tr>
									</table>
								{% endfor %}

								<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top:28px;">
									<tr>
										<td align="center">
											<a href="{{ url('app_my_tickets') }}" style="display:inline-block;background-color:#6366F9;color:#ffffff;padding:14px 36px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;">
												Afficher mes réservations
											</a>
										</td>
									</tr>
								</table>

								<p style="color:#a1a1a1;font-size:12px;text-align:center;margin:24px 0 0;line-height:1.5;">
									Présentez votre QR code le jour de l'enchère pour accéder à la salle.
								</p>
							</td>
						</tr>

						{# Footer #}
						<tr>
							<td style="padding:20px 40px;border-top:1px solid #2a2a2a;text-align:center;">
								<p style="color:#666;font-size:11px;margin:0;">© 2026 Carte Blanche Platform — Tous droits réservés</p>
							</td>
						</tr>

					</table>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>

	</body>
</html>
